  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>No panic! You don't need to know how assemble Rubik's cube.</i></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong><i>We tried to make the game accessible to everyone.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/08e27cf6a89dada0bcad4c24bdd78d30.avif?t=1754479234\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evil Obfus has disturbed the peace that has reigned in Cubindom for centuries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate the faces of the Rubik's Cube to restore the usual order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the wonderful world and take a break from everyday activities. At the same time, Rubicon challenges those who are eager to test themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think carefully about your actions to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/1f58418b830ec8ba27c3ba8adbdeb9c8.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=250 /></span>In the game you will face two types of levels:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cunning Obfus confused the brave knights and placed his dangerous henchmen to prevent them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help the brave warriors find their way to the tower.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a8b14b704c01384bff9c399b394cd4a7.poster.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a8b14b704c01384bff9c399b394cd4a7.webm?t=1754479234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a8b14b704c01384bff9c399b394cd4a7.mp4?t=1754479234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Envious Obfus violated the integrity of the castle walls.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the inhabitants from danger by connecting walls of the same color to each other.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a43f68604044317b8fabb8e84f5dd96b.poster.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a43f68604044317b8fabb8e84f5dd96b.webm?t=1754479234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a43f68604044317b8fabb8e84f5dd96b.mp4?t=1754479234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/0bddace23d6f466048d06592458f1451.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=250 /></span>This game was invented by a schoolboy, and implemented by a student with the help of people from various areas of game development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have any questions, found translation inaccuracies or game bugs do not hesitate to contact us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will try to answer you promptly and solve the problems that have arisen.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>No panic! You don't need to know how assemble Rubik's cube.</i></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong><i>We tried to make the game accessible to everyone.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/08e27cf6a89dada0bcad4c24bdd78d30.avif?t=1754479234\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evil Obfus has disturbed the peace that has reigned in Cubindom for centuries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate the faces of the Rubik's Cube to restore the usual order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the wonderful world and take a break from everyday activities. At the same time, Rubicon challenges those who are eager to test themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think carefully about your actions to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/1f58418b830ec8ba27c3ba8adbdeb9c8.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=250 /></span>In the game you will face two types of levels:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cunning Obfus confused the brave knights and placed his dangerous henchmen to prevent them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help the brave warriors find their way to the tower.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a8b14b704c01384bff9c399b394cd4a7.poster.avif?t=1754479234\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/extras/a8b14b704c01384bff9c399b394cd4a7.webm?t=1754479234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452790/e